description_en:
&quot;Natural Therapy is a definition of ANNART botanic founded by a pharmacist who is expertise
in pharmaceutical sciences, herbology, and aromatherapy. Proudly presented an alternative
product that is originated from nature, by blending various types of oils that help relieves symptoms such as headache, migraine, backache, knee pain, trigger finger, neck and shoulder stiffness, tiredness, work performance decreased or insomnia.&quot;

