description_en:
&quot;Founded by two Thai designers, Saprang means blooming in Thai. The word represents the identity
of the jewelry-art collection, organic forms with floral patterns that fused with various techniques
of silversmith crafts and design. For Saprang, the inner lining of nature is a key to all ideas. Forms and lines are reinterpreted with appropriated materials, craftsmanship and individual skill of artisans that expresses the whole combination into wearable jewelry collections.&quot;

