description_en:
&quot;The blend of “Art – Craft – Space” design gallery, a place where the knowledge and experience in
handcrafting and industrial fields meet, creating the remarkable aesthetics of textures and shapes.
Under the “Wabi-sabi” philosophy, SUMPHAT Gallery had established worthwhile designs and traditional techniques in a new dimension in hopes to improve the lives of the local and encourage the local community and art to connect sustainably.&quot;

